---
title: SuperQuick Teriyaki Turkey Ramen Bowls  with Bell Peppers and Sugar Snap Peas
description: This teriyaki turkey stir fry features vibrant bell peppers and crisp sugar snap peas tossed in a delicious, tangy sauce and served over a bed of chewy ramen noodles. If you're looking for a meal with bold flavours and satisfying textures, you've found it — and it's ready in just 15 minutes.

